nMenu\"><a class=\"zDocsExportItem zDocsExportTopicButton\" href=\"#\" id=\"singlePdf\" role=\"button\">Save selected topic</a><a class=\"zDocsExportItem zDocsExportSubtopicsButton\" href=\"#\" id=\"pdfWithChildren\" role=\"button\">Save selected topic and subtopics</a><a class=\"zDocsExportItem zDocsExportBundleButton\" href=\"#\" id=\"wholeBundlePdf\" role=\"button\">Save entire publication</a></div></div><div class=\"zDocsTopicShare zDocsShareButton\" role=\"listitem\"><span aria-expanded=\"false\" aria-label=\"Share\" class=\"d-none d-lg-flex zDocsShareDialogButton\" data-toggle=\"dropdown\" data-tooltip-content=\"Share\" data-tooltip-id=\"zDocsTopicActionsTooltip\" role=\"button\" tabindex=\"0\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-share\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-share\"></use></svg></span><span class=\"d-lg-none zDocsShareDialogButton\" role=\"button\" tabindex=\"0\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-share\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-share\"></use></svg>Share</span><div class=\"dropdown-menu zDocsDropdownMenu\"><a class=\"dropdown-item zDocsShareButton zDocsShareEmail\" href=\"#\" role=\"button\"><span>Email Link</span></a><a class=\"dropdown-item zDocsShareButton zDocsShareLink\" href=\"#\" role=\"button\"><span>Copy Link</span></a></div></div><div class=\"zDocsFeedback zDocsFeedback zDocsTopicFeedback\" role=\"listitem\"><span aria-label=\"Feedback\" class=\"zDocsFeedbackButton d-none d-lg-flex\" data-backdrop=\"static\" data-target=\"#feedbackModal_main_3617504\" data-toggle=\"modal\" data-tooltip-content=\"Feedback\" data-tooltip-id=\"zDocsTopicActionsTooltip\" role=\"button\" tabindex=\"0\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-feedback\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-feedback\"></use></svg></span><span class=\"d-lg-none d-flex zDocsFeedbackButton\" data-backdrop=\"static\" data-return-focus=\"#zDocsTopicActionsMobile\" data-target=\"#feedbackModal_main_3617504\" data-toggle=\"modal\" role=\"button\" tabindex=\"0\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-feedback\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-feedback\"></use></svg><span class=\"zDocsFeedbackButtonText\"> Feedback</span></span></div></div><div class=\"zDocsTopicActionsMobile\"><button aria-label=\"Show topic actions\" data-toggle=\"dropdown\" id=\"zDocsTopicActionsMobile\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-ellipsis-h\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-ellipsis-h\"></use></svg></button><div class=\"dropdown-menu zDocsDropdownMenu zDocsTopicActionsMobileDropdown dropdown-menu-right\"></div></div><div style=\"flex-basis: 100%; height: 0px;\"></div><ul class=\"zDocsTopicPageDetails\"><li class=\"zDocsTopicPageDate css-cinqea\">Last Updated<span class=\"css-cinqea\">Jan 06, 2025</span></li><li class=\"zDocsAiTopicSummaryDetailsItem\"><button class=\"zDocsAiTopicSummaryButton\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-topic-summary\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-topic-summary\"></use></svg>Summarize</button></li><li class=\"spacer\" role=\"presentation\"></li><div class=\"zDocsLabelWrapper\"><ul><li class=\"zDocsLabel\"><a aria-describedby=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" class=\"css-ettsdk\" data-tooltip-content=\"Search all site by tag: Uniface\" data-tooltip-id=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" href=\"/de-DE/search?labelkey=prod_uniface\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-label=\"Tag\" class=\"ico-tag\" role=\"img\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-tag\"></use></svg>Uniface</a></li><li class=\"zDocsLabel\"><a aria-describedby=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" class=\"css-ettsdk\" data-tooltip-content=\"Search all site by tag: 10.4\" data-tooltip-id=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" href=\"/de-DE/search?labelkey=uniface_10.4\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-label=\"Tag\" class=\"ico-tag\" role=\"img\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-tag\"></use></svg>10.4</a></li></ul></div></ul></header><div class=\"zDocsTopicPageBody\" data-prismjs-copy=\"Copy\" data-prismjs-copy-error=\"Copy failed! Use Ctrl + C instead.\" data-prismjs-copy-success=\"Copied!\"><div class=\"zDocsTopicPageBodyContent\" dir=\"ltr\"><div id=\"zDocsAiSummaryContaineruniface_104zwi1665702662755.html\"></div><div><article class=\"hascomments\" data-page=\"bundle:uniface_104/enus/zwi1665702662755.html\" id=\"bundle:uniface_104/enus/zwi1665702662755.html\"><main role=\"main\"><article aria-labelledby=\"ariaid-title1\" class=\"dita\" id=\"zwi1665702662755\" role=\"article\">\n<h1 class=\"title topictitle1\" id=\"ariaid-title1\">\n      Item\n </h1>\n<div class=\"body conbody\"><p class=\"shortdesc\">Label of a menu item (including optional icon), as displayed in the menu bar or menu. To include an icon, use a GOLD ! between the image and text values.\n </p>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"zwi1665702662755__p_d110180e1_d110181e1_d110182e1\">{<code class=\"ph codeph\">@<var class=\"keyword varname\">ImageName</var></code> |\n               <code class=\"ph codeph\">^<var class=\"keyword varname\">GlyphName</var></code><code class=\"ph codeph\"><span class=\"ph gold\">;</span>}</code><var class=\"keyword varname\">ItemText</var></p>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"zwi1665702662755__p_d110183e1_d110184e1_d110185e1\">Icon only:\n            <code class=\"ph codeph\">@<var class=\"keyword varname\">ImageName</var></code> |\n            <code class=\"ph codeph\">^<var class=\"keyword varname\">GlyphName</var></code><code class=\"ph codeph\"><span class=\"ph gold\">;</span>\"\"</code></p>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"zwi1665702662755__section_vpw_ckl_cxb\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d723275e85\">Description</h2>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"zwi1665702662755__p_d110189e1_d110190e1_d110191e1\">This property, rather than the\n               <span class=\"ph uicontrol\">Name</span> of a referenced menu, determines the actual text of the\n            menu option.</p>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"zwi1665702662755__p_d110192e1_d110193e1_d110194e1\">By default, the first character of the\n               <span class=\"ph uicontrol\">Item</span> property serves as a mnemonic identifier for that item.\n            To use a different character, a percent sign (%) must be included before the character,\n            for example <code class=\"ph codeph\">Fil%e</code> to display File.</p>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"zwi1665702662755__p_d110195e1_d110196e1_d110197e1\">To precede the Item text with an icon, you can\n            specify an image or glyph and the text as a GOLD ! (exclamation mark) separated\n            list:</p>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"zwi1665702662755__p_d110198e1_d110199e1_d110200e1\">{<code class=\"ph codeph\">@</code><var class=\"keyword varname\">Image</var> |\n               <code class=\"ph codeph\">^</code><var class=\"keyword varname\">Glyph</var>\n<span class=\"ph gold\">!</span> } <var class=\"keyword varname\">OptionText</var></p>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"zwi1665702662755__p_d110201e1_d110202e1_d110203e1\">For example: <code class=\"ph codeph\">@file_open.png<span class=\"ph gold\">!</span>Open file</code></p>\n<figure class=\"fig fignone\" id=\"zwi1665702662755__fig_d110204e1_d110205e1_d110206e1\"><figcaption><span class=\"fig--title-label\">Figure 1. </span>Specifying an Image in Menu Option</figcaption>\n<img alt=\"Image\" class=\"image\" id=\"zwi1665702662755__image_wtc_jkl_cxb\" src=\"https://docs-be.rocketsoftware.com/bundle/uniface_104/page/imaginmenu.png?_LANG=enus\"/>\n</figure>\n<div class=\"note important note_important\" id=\"zwi1665702662755__note_scv_hkl_cxb\"><span class=\"note__title\">Important:</span> At runtime, icons are displayed in menus only\n            if at least one menu property is set in the application <span class=\"ph filepath\">.ini</span> file.\n            For example:</div>\n<div class=\"code-toolbar\"><pre class=\"pre language-plaintext\" id=\"zwi1665702662755__pre_tcv_hkl_cxb\" tabindex=\"0\"><code class=\"language-plaintext\">;usys.ini\n[application]\nMenu = umenu(backcolor=control)</code></pre><div class=\"toolbar\"><div class=\"toolbar-item\"><button class=\"copy-to-clipboard-button\" data-copy-state=\"copy\" type=\"button\"><span>Copy</span></button></div></div></div>\n</section>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"zwi1665702662755__section_adb_2kl_cxb\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d723275e157\">Applies To</h2>\n<ul class=\"ul\" id=\"zwi1665702662755__ul_hzd_mkl_cxb\">\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"zwi1665702662755__li_d42638e1_d42639e1_d42640e1\"><a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"bxw1705577952463.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/bxw1705577952463.html\" title=\"A menu item can be a menu option that results in an action, a reference to another menu, such as a cascaded menu or included menu, or a separator for grouping items. Menu items have associated triggers in which to program the conditions under which they are displayed and the action they perform.\">Menu Items</a>\n</li>\n</ul>\n</section>\n</div>\n</article></main></article>\n</div></div><div class=\"contentPlaceholder\" style=\"height: 500px;\"><div class=\"contentContainer zDocsSideBoxes\"><div><h5 aria-level=\"5\" class=\"css-g931ng\">Related Links</h5><ul><li><a class=\"css-ettsdk\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/crm1665702872883.html\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-related-link\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-related-link\"></use></svg>Menu Objects</a><p>Uniface enables you to define menu bar, drop-down menu, and pop-up menu objects for use in Windows applications.</p></li><li><a class=\"css-ettsdk\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/bxw1705577952463.html\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-related-link\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-related-link\"></use></svg>Menu Items</a><p>A menu item can be a menu option that results in an action, a reference to another menu, such as a cascaded menu or included menu, or a separator for grouping items. Menu items have associated triggers in which to program the conditions under which they are displayed and the action they perform.</p></li><li><a class=\"css-ettsdk\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/mwc1665702671394.html\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-related-link\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-related-link\"></use></svg>Menu</a><p>Set the font, color, and image properties for menus.</p></li></ul></div></div></div></div><div class=\"bottomFeedback\"><div aria-labelledby=\"bottomFeedbackText\" class=\"bottomFeedbackContent\" role=\"group\"><span class=\"bottomFeedbackText\" id=\"bottomFeedbackText\">Was this topic helpful?</span><div class=\"bottomFeedbackButtonGroup\"><a data-backdrop=\"static\" data-target=\"#feedbackModal_bottom_3617504\" data-toggle=\"modal\" href=\"#\" role=\"button\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-thumbs-up\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-thumbs-up\"></use></svg><span>Like</span></a><a data-backdrop=\"static\" data-target=\"#feedbackModal_bottom_3617504\" data-toggle=\"modal\" href=\"#\" role=\"button\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-thumbs-down\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-thumbs-down\"></use></svg><span>Dislike</span></a></div></div></div><div style=\"position: fixed; bottom: 170px; right: 70px; cursor: pointer; transition-duration: 0.2s; transition-timing-function: linear; transition-delay: 0s; z-index: 3; opacity: 0; visibility: hidden; transition-property: opacity, visibility;\"><button aria-label=\"Scroll to top\" class=\"zDocsScrollTopBtn\" data-tooltip-content=\"Scroll to top\" data-tooltip-id=\"zDocsBackToTopToolTip\" id=\"zDocsScrollToTop\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-next\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-next\"></use></svg></button></div></body></html>", "text": "Item Add to My Topics Add selected topic and subtopics Add Topic & Subtopics with topic head Add entire publication Watch Download PDF Save selected topic Save selected topic and subtopics Save entire publication Share Email Link Copy Link Feedback Last Updated Jan 06, 2025 Summarize Uniface 10.4 Item Label of a menu item (including optional icon), as displayed in the menu bar or menu. To include an icon, use a GOLD ! between the image and text values. { @ ImageName | ^ GlyphName ; } ItemText Icon only: @ ImageName | ^ GlyphName ; \"\" Description This property, rather than the Name of a referenced menu, determines the actual text of the menu option. By default, the first character of the Item property serves as a mnemonic identifier for that item. To use a different character, a percent sign (%) must be included before the character, for example Fil%e to display File. To precede the Item text with an icon, you can specify an image or glyph and the text as a GOLD ! (exclamation mark) separated list: { @ Image | ^ Glyph ! } OptionText For example: @file_open.png ! Open file Figure 1. Specifying an Image in Menu Option Important: At runtime, icons are displayed in menus only if at least one menu property is set in the application .ini file. For example: ;usys.ini [application] Menu = umenu(backcolor=control) Copy Applies To Menu Items Related Links Menu Objects Uniface enables you to define menu bar, drop-down menu, and pop-up menu objects for use in Windows applications. Menu Items A menu item can be a menu option that results in an action, a reference to another menu, such as a cascaded menu or included menu, or a separator for grouping items. Menu items have associated triggers in which to program the conditions under which they are displayed and the action they perform. Menu Set the font, color, and image properties for menus. Was this topic helpful? Like Dislike"}